- **Type:** Operations (recurring)
- **Source of record:** Pocketsmith (transactions, budgets, forecasts). Finals to `onedrive://OneDrive-Personal/04_Finance/`.

## What this is
The money-management front. Two ledgers kept separate: Nick personally, and Nicholas Wood Digital
Consulting (ABN + PTY LTD, which has GST). Turns transactions into a picture plus a recommendation,
and removes the manual reconcile and review work. Cashflow and runway are first-class right now while
Nick is between roles and job-hunting.

